description: Application for a Non Material Amendment (S96a) to vary condition no.26 (Approved Drawings) of planning permission ref. 164694FUL  dated 01/09/2017 as amended by 184888VAR dated 10.01.2020, for Phased redevelopment comprising a residential-led mixed use masterplan incorporating residential; flexible commercial and community floorspace, in use classes A1/A2/A3/A4/A5/B1/D1 and/or D2 including a primary school and nursery; a pedestrian/cycle bridge across the Grand Union Canal; car and cycle parking; site wide landscaping and associated works, including highway works; following the demolition of buildings and structures on the site  - Amendment seeks non-material alterations to Block 3 comprising internal layout changes, changes to unit mix, external alterations, addition of balconies, addition of a mezzanine floor, and relocation of roof terrace
